1398
01:40:22,020 --> 01:40:23,693
We can't leave her like that.

1399
01:40:24,660 --> 01:40:25,889
Where is she?

1400
01:40:26,020 --> 01:40:28,489
I didn't want to worry you, but...

1401
01:40:29,540 --> 01:40:32,180
