Sorry about the messages...

1408
01:42:47,660 --> 01:42:48,696
Really?

1409
01:42:49,860 --> 01:42:51,897
Really? Is she...

1410
01:42:52,420 --> 01:42:53,649
How is she?

1411
01:42:56,780 --> 01:42:58,373
We'll be right there.

1412
01:43:00,640 --> 01:43:02,074
She's outside my house.

1413
01:43:02,840 --> 01:43:06,038
He found her on the sidewalk.
Unconscious.

1414
01:43:06,160 --> 01:43:07,389
She doesn't react.

1415
01:43:08,240 --> 01:43:09,515
